---
import Page from "../layouts/Page.astro";
import Head from "../layouts/Head.astro";
import Hero from "../layouts/HomeHero.astro";
import Bullet from "../components/Bullet.astro";

const meta = {
  title: "Web-o-Reviews",
  description: "Akshay Ghate's Portfolio and future blog.",
};
---

<Page>
  <Head slot="head" {meta} />
  <Hero />
  <main id="content-wrapper" class=":uno: mxa max-w-7xl py-12 px-8">
    <div class=":uno: space-y-24 leading-relaxed grid place-items-center">
      <div class=":uno: max-w-prose">
        <h3 class=":uno: font-display my-5 mx-3 text-center text-f-2xl fw700">
          What I do
        </h3>
        <p
          class=":uno: first-letter:text-f-xl first-letter:fw600 first-letter:text-radixcrimson-11"
        >
          I offer web design services to businesses and individuals. I see that
          my service fits within your budget and/or time constraints. Once my
          web design services are complete, I will also provide you with ongoing
          web support for your new site. Especially as your company grows and
          your online information and written content on your website change.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div
          class=":uno: rounded-full flex bg-radixteal-3 h-16 ml-4 p-3 ring-2 ring-radixteal-7 ring-offset-radixteal-7 ring-offset-8 w-16 z-10 relative items-center justify-center"
        >
          <span
            class=":uno: h-12 text-radixteal-12 w-12 i-solar:code-line-duotone"
            role="none"></span>
        </div>
        <div
          class=":uno: bg-radixteal-2 border rounded-md border-radixteal-6 text-radixteal-11 shadow-md -mt-8 py-8 px-4 md:p-8"
        >
          <div class=":uno: text-f-lg py-4 fw600">Web Developement</div>
          <p>
            HTML / CSS, Javascript Animation, Responsive website, Support and
            Maintenance.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3
          class=":uno: font-display mx-3 mt-5 text-f-xl text-center mb-14 fw700"
        >
          Our Process
        </h3>
        <ul
          class=":uno: grid gap-24 grid-cols-1 place-items-stretch sm:gap-x-6 sm:gap-y-12 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3"
        >
          <li
            class=":uno: bg-radixgray-2 border rounded-md border-radixgray-6 shadow-md py-4 px-6 lg:px-8"
          >
            <div
              class=":uno: rounded-full flex mxa bg-radixblue-3 h-16 -mt-12 p-3 ring-2 ring-radixblue-7 ring-offset-radixblue-7 ring-offset-8 w-16 z-10 items-center justify-center"
            >
              <span
                class=":uno: h-12 text-radixblue-12 w-12 i-solar:chat-line-linear"
                role="none"></span>
            </div>
            <h4
              class=":uno: border-b-2 border-radixblue-6 my-4 text-f-lg fw600"
            >
              1. Discuss
            </h4>
            <p>
              To define the goals. What objective does the website need to
              accomplish? What problem does it solve?
            </p>
            <p class=":uno: my-2 text-f-sm uppercase fw600">Key Process:</p>
            <div class=":uno: flex flex-wrap p-1 justify-start">
              <Bullet
                color="bg-radixblue-1 border-radixblue-6 text-radixblue-11"
              >
                Brainstorming
              </Bullet>
              <Bullet
                color="bg-radixblue-1 border-radixblue-6 text-radixblue-11"
              >
                Define a Problem
              </Bullet>
              <Bullet
                color="bg-radixblue-1 border-radixblue-6 text-radixblue-11"
              >
                Primary Aim
              </Bullet>
              <Bullet
                color="bg-radixblue-1 border-radixblue-6 text-radixblue-11"
              >
                Analysis
              </Bullet>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li
            class=":uno: bg-radixgray-2 border rounded-md border-radixgray-6 shadow-md py-4 px-6 lg:px-8"
          >
            <div
              class=":uno: rounded-full flex mxa bg-radixpurple-3 h-16 -mt-12 p-3 ring-2 ring-radixpurple-7 ring-offset-radixpurple-7 ring-offset-8 w-16 z-10 items-center justify-center"
            >
              <span
                class=":uno: h-12 text-radixpurple-12 w-12 i-solar:checklist-bold-duotone"
                role="none"></span>
            </div>
            <h4
              class=":uno: border-b-2 border-radixpurple-6 my-4 text-f-lg fw600"
            >
              2. Planning
            </h4>
            <p>
              To decide the technical aspects of the project, such as the
              selection of the tech stack to build the website and content
              strategy planning.
            </p>
            <p class=":uno: my-2 text-f-sm uppercase fw600">Key Process:</p>
            <div class=":uno: flex flex-wrap p-1 justify-start">
              <Bullet
                color="bg-radixpurple-1 border-radixpurple-6 text-radixpurple-11"
              >
                Content Developement Strategy
              </Bullet>
              <Bullet
                color="bg-radixpurple-1 border-radixpurple-6 text-radixpurple-11"
              >
                SEO Strategy
              </Bullet>
              <Bullet
                color="bg-radixpurple-1 border-radixpurple-6 text-radixpurple-11"
              >
                Technology stacks
              </Bullet>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li
            class=":uno: bg-radixgray-2 border rounded-md border-radixgray-6 shadow-md py-4 px-6 lg:px-8"
          >
            <div
              class=":uno: rounded-full flex mxa bg-radixtomato-3 h-16 -mt-12 p-3 ring-2 ring-radixtomato-7 ring-offset-radixtomato-7 ring-offset-8 w-16 z-10 relative items-center justify-center"
            >
              <span
                class=":uno: h-12 text-radixtomato-12 w-12 i-solar:pallete-2-outline"
                role="none"></span>
            </div>
            <h4
              class=":uno: border-b-2 border-radixtomato-6 my-4 text-f-lg fw600"
            >
              3. Designing
            </h4>
            <p>
              To design the color scheme, logo design, and other interactive
              design elements to be incorporated on the website and figure out
              the structure.
            </p>
            <p class=":uno: my-2 text-f-sm uppercase fw600">Key Process:</p>
            <div class=":uno: flex flex-wrap p-1 justify-start">
              <Bullet
                color="bg-radixtomato-1 border-radixtomato-6 text-radixtomato-11"
              >
                Prototyping
              </Bullet>
              <Bullet
                color="bg-radixtomato-1 border-radixtomato-6 text-radixtomato-11"
              >
                Designing
              </Bullet>
              <Bullet
                color="bg-radixtomato-1 border-radixtomato-6 text-radixtomato-11"
              >
                Developement
              </Bullet>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li
            class=":uno: bg-radixgray-2 border rounded-md border-radixgray-6 shadow-md py-4 px-6 lg:px-8"
          >
            <div
              class=":uno: rounded-full flex mxa bg-radixyellow-3 h-16 -mt-12 p-3 ring-2 ring-radixyellow-7 ring-offset-radixyellow-7 ring-offset-8 w-16 z-10 relative items-center justify-center"
            >
              <span
                class=":uno: h-12 text-radixyellow-12 w-12 i-solar:test-tube-minimalistic-line-duotone"
                role="none"></span>
            </div>
            <h4
              class=":uno: border-b-2 border-radixyellow-6 my-4 text-f-lg fw600"
            >
              4. Testing
            </h4>
            <p>
              Website testing consists of several different tests, including
              functionality, usability, interface, compatibility, etc.
            </p>
            <p class=":uno: my-2 text-f-sm uppercase fw600">Key Process:</p>
            <div class=":uno: flex flex-wrap p-1 justify-start">
              <Bullet
                color="bg-radixyellow-1 border-radixyellow-6 text-radixyellow-11"
              >
                Testing
              </Bullet>
              <Bullet
                color="bg-radixyellow-1 border-radixyellow-6 text-radixyellow-11"
              >
                Compatibility
              </Bullet>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li
            class=":uno: bg-radixgray-2 border rounded-md border-radixgray-6 shadow-md py-4 px-6 sm:col-span-2 lg:px-8"
          >
            <div
              class=":uno: rounded-full flex mxa bg-radixgreen-3 h-16 -mt-12 p-3 ring-2 ring-radixgreen-7 ring-offset-radixgreen-7 ring-offset-8 w-16 z-10 relative items-center justify-center"
            >
              <span
                class=":uno: h-12 text-radixgreen-12 w-12 i-solar:rocket-line-duotone"
                role="none"></span>
            </div>
            <h4
              class=":uno: border-b-2 border-radixgreen-6 my-4 text-f-lg fw600"
            >
              5. Launching and Maintenance
            </h4>
            <p>
              Launching the website involves transferring it from my local
              server to a live server. The launch isn't the end of the
              development journey. The maintenance phase is what follows and is
              critical for the website to be successfully up and running.
            </p>
            <p class=":uno: my-2 text-f-sm uppercase fw600">Key Process:</p>
            <div class=":uno: flex flex-wrap p-1 justify-start">
              <Bullet
                color="bg-radixgreen-1 border-radixgreen-6 text-radixgreen-11"
              >
                Testing
              </Bullet>
              <Bullet
                color="bg-radixgreen-1 border-radixgreen-6 text-radixgreen-11"
              >
                Maintenance
              </Bullet>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Page>
